flowchart TD
    start([Start]) --> openReturnTab[Librarian opens Cho xac nhan tra tab]
    openReturnTab --> checkRole{Logged in as librarian?}
    checkRole -->|No| denyAccess[Redirect to login or show access denied]
    denyAccess --> endNode([End])
    checkRole -->|Yes| loadRequests[Load pending return requests]

    loadRequests --> receiveBook[Receive physical book from reader]
    receiveBook --> clickConfirm[Click Xac nhan tra]
    clickConfirm --> chooseCondition{Book condition?}

    chooseCondition -->|Binh thuong| normalReturn[Confirm normal return]
    chooseCondition -->|Hu hong| damagedReturn[Select damage fine level and enter note]
    chooseCondition -->|Mat| lostReturn[Select lost fine level and enter note]

    normalReturn --> markReturned[Update borrow status = Da tra]
    markReturned --> increaseAvailable[Increase available quantity]
    increaseAvailable --> decreaseBorrowed[Decrease borrowed quantity]
    decreaseBorrowed --> endNode

    damagedReturn --> validateDamaged{Fine selected and note provided?}
    validateDamaged -->|No| damagedError[Show validation errors]
    damagedError --> damagedReturn
    validateDamaged -->|Yes| addLateFineIfNeeded{Late return also applies?}
    addLateFineIfNeeded -->|Yes| createLateFine[Create late fine]
    addLateFineIfNeeded -->|No| createDamageFine[Create damage fine]
    createLateFine --> createDamageFine
    createDamageFine --> markReturnedDamaged[Update borrow status = Da tra]
    markReturnedDamaged --> endNode

    lostReturn --> validateLost{Fine selected and note provided?}
    validateLost -->|No| lostError[Show validation errors]
    lostError --> lostReturn
    validateLost -->|Yes| createLostFine[Create lost fine]
    createLostFine --> markReturnedLost[Update borrow status = Da tra]
    markReturnedLost --> endNode
